### Layer 2: LLM Wrapper

#### [MODIFY] [openrouter.ts](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/packages/llm/src/openrouter.ts)
Complete rewrite with new return types:

| Function | Old Return | New Return |
|----------|-----------|------------|
| [OpenRouterQuery](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/packages/llm/src/openrouter.ts#91-180) (non-stream) | `string` | `{ text, usage: { inputTokens, outputTokens, totalTokens } }` |
| [OpenRouterQuery](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/packages/llm/src/openrouter.ts#91-180) (stream) | `AsyncIterable<string>` | `{ stream, getUsage: () => Promise<AIUsage> }` |
| [OpenRouterEmbed](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/packages/llm/src/openai.ts#158-188) | `number[][]` | `{ embeddings, usage: { totalTokens } }` |

Uses function overloads for type-safe streaming vs non-streaming dispatch. Non-streaming uses `getResponse()` to extract `response.usage`. Streaming defers usage via [getUsage()](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/packages/llm/src/openrouter.ts#140-154) callback (called after stream completes).

#### [MODIFY] [package.json](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/packages/llm/package.json)
Added `types` paths to exports for dev-time type resolution.

---

### Layer 3: Cost Calculation

#### [NEW] [cost.ts](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/utils/cost.ts)
[calculateCost(modelId, inputTokens, outputTokens)](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/utils/cost.ts#6-41) — uses prices from [openrouter_models.ts](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/packages/llm/src/data/openrouter_models.ts) (per-million-tokens). Falls back to $1/$2 per million for unknown models.

