### Layer 4: Services

#### [NEW] [credits.service.ts](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/credits.service.ts)
- [getBalance(orgId)](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/credits.service.ts#9-20) / [hasEnoughCredits(orgId, cost)](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/credits.service.ts#21-31)
- [deductCredits({orgId, amount, ...})](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/credits.service.ts#36-87) — **atomic**: single SQL `UPDATE ... WHERE balance >= amount`
- [addCredits({orgId, amount, type, ...})](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/credits.service.ts#88-127) — for topup/refund/adjustment
- [getTransactionHistory(orgId, options)](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/credits.service.ts#132-158)

#### [NEW] [usage.service.ts](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/usage.service.ts)
- [logUsageAndDeduct(input)](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/usage.service.ts#42-97) — single entry point: calculates cost → inserts log → deducts credits
- [getUsageStats(orgId, {from, to})](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/usage.service.ts#102-165) — aggregated (total cost, by model, by operation)
- [getUsageHistory(orgId, options)](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/usage.service.ts#166-196) — paginated log

#### [MODIFY] [rag.service.ts](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/rag.service.ts)
- [queryRAG](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/rag.service.ts#236-303) / [queryRAGStream](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/rag.service.ts#304-401) / [searchChunks](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/rag.service.ts#159-235) now accept `organizationId` + `userId`
- After each AI call, logs usage via [logUsageAndDeduct()](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/usage.service.ts#42-97) (fire-and-forget with `.catch()`)
- [queryRAGStream](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/rag.service.ts#304-401) yields a new `{ type: "usage", data: AIUsage }` event before `done`
- [indexDocument](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/rag.service.ts#75-151) passes org context to job data

