### Layer 5: Middleware

#### [MODIFY] [middleware.ts](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/router/middleware.ts)
Two new procedures:
- **`orgProcedure`** — requires `session.activeOrganizationId`, injects `organizationId` into context
- **`creditsProcedure`** — extends orgProcedure, checks `balance >= 0.0001` before proceeding

---

### Layer 6: Routes

#### [NEW] [credits.routes.ts](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/router/routes/credits.routes.ts)
- `GET /credits/balance` — org balance
- `GET /credits/transactions` — paginated transaction history (type filter)
- `POST /credits/topup` — admin-only, manual balance addition

#### [NEW] [usage.routes.ts](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/router/routes/usage.routes.ts)
- `GET /usage/stats` — aggregated stats with date range filter
- `GET /usage/history` — paginated usage log (operation type + user filters)

