[query](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/rag.service.ts#236-303), `queryStream`, [search](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/services/rag.service.ts#159-235) → switched from `authProcedure` to `creditsProcedure`, pass `organizationId`/`userId` to service.

#### [MODIFY] [document.routes.ts](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/router/routes/document.routes.ts)
[createDocument](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/jobs/document/document.worker.ts#363-399) → `creditsProcedure`, passes `organizationId` to indexing job.

#### [MODIFY] [index.ts](file:///home/nas/personal_projects/foxmayn_ai/apps/api/src/router/index.ts)
Registered `credits` and `usage` route groups.

